<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٣٢ <span class="c2">(م)</span> - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4316">عُثْمَانُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ </a>مِثْلَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَابَعَهُ بِشْرٌ عَنِ ابْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ عَنْ شُعْبَةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَتَابَعَهُ ابْنُ جُرَيْجٍ، عَنْ عَبْدَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ شَقِيقٍ:</span> سَمِعْتُ عَبْدَ اللهِ: سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>